News24 Correspondent Two SANDF members were killed in an accident (Supplied, Limpopo police). Multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; User Galleries &nbsp; &nbsp; News in Pictures Send us your pictures &nbsp; &nbsp; Send us your stories Makhado- Two SANDF members were killed when three trucks collided on the N1 near Louis Trichardt on Thursday, Limpopo police said. &nbsp; A SANDF and another truck were travelling towards the town when the driver of a north-bound Hino truck lost control and crashed into them, Brigadier Motlafela Mojapelo said.One of the SANDF members died on the scene. The other died shortly after arrival at a local hospital.24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.